data.description: MUST SEE! Beautiful 2 bed, 2 bath single family home in 55+ gated community with clubhouse and pool in Avon Park. A/C only 2 years old. Escape to this charming 2 bedroom/2 bath home in the Oaks Village retirement community. Nestled a short distance from US 27, medical offices, local shops and eateries, this quiet gated community provides the feeling of seclusion with the convenience of downtown living. The low HOA provides you access to the community pool, community center and also pays for lawn maintenance and irrigation. Perks of living in this paradise are the landscaped grounds, daily exercise, social activities. If you are looking to retire and live the easy life, this home is for you! Seller financing available.
